    <description>
MasterChief is a comprehensive, modular enterprise DevOps automation platform for managing infrastructure, deployments, and operations at scale.

## Features
- Module Loader System with hot-reload capabilities
- Configuration Engine with environment support
- Event Bus for event-driven architecture
- Powerful CLI tool
- Terraform Azure Modules
- Ansible Automation
- PowerShell DSC
- Kubernetes support
- ChatOps and IRC Bot
- Web IDE with Monaco Editor
- System Management tools
- Observability dashboards
- Security and Compliance tools

## Requirements
- Python 3.10 or higher
- Node.js 18 or higher (optional)
